gw.api.bean.compare.ui

Class DiffDisplay

  • gw.api.bean.compare.ui.DiffDisplay

  • public class DiffDisplay
    Represents a policy difference as it appears in the policy refresh comparison screen. It provides everything necessary to display the difference. Operations on a DiffDisplay are not recursive, for example {@link #getType()} does not examine their children.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      String Label
      the displayable value for the Diff being displayed.
      String NewValue
      the new Policy value for the Diff being displayed.
      String OldValue
      the old Policy value for the Diff being displayed.
      DiffDisplay.Type Type
      the Type (added, changed, removed, unchanged) that the Diff represents.
